in the simplest way possible.

71
00:05:12.563 --> 00:05:17.623
Basically, you'd press a button and
it would either say you've won or

72
00:05:17.623 --> 00:05:20.505
you've lost and that'd be it, right?

73
00:05:20.505 --> 00:05:24.113
In fact, it could be even more
seamless an experience and

74
00:05:24.113 --> 00:05:25.923
that you could walk up to it.

75
00:05:25.923 --> 00:05:30.671
And there could be a sensor on it
that detects you walking up and

76
00:05:30.671 --> 00:05:33.515
