I adopt to get this right.

86
00:06:12.723 --> 00:06:17.360
I don't think I'm a natural
creative designer in may be

87
00:06:17.360 --> 00:06:19.836
the way that some people are.

88
00:06:19.836 --> 00:06:26.117
And so I've kind of reduced it down to
a process that I can kind of follow.

89
00:06:26.117 --> 00:06:31.798
