00:08:53.043 --> 00:08:58.188
I'll call design delighted and
they're a really good way of putting

124
00:08:58.188 --> 00:09:02.723
people in a positive mindset
about your brand or direction.

125
00:09:02.723 --> 00:09:07.641
And these do take a little bit of
thought and a little bit of fun but

126
00:09:07.641 --> 00:09:10.111
